@startuml uc11-rollback-stream
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
title UC11 - Force / roll back a stream

actor Operator as op

rectangle "ROTA server (ota-store)" {
  usecase "Hand-edit\nchannels/<stream>.json" as UC11
  usecase "Point stream to an older\nstaged version" as OLD
  usecase "Pin affected units\ninstead" as PINALT
}

op --> UC11
UC11 ..> OLD : <<include>>
PINALT ..> UC11 : <<extend>>\n(per-unit alternative)

note right of OLD
  The retriever refuses to
  downgrade, so rollback is
  always an explicit human act
end note
@enduml
